reference "eq:covariance_sensitivity_general"

\end_inset

, one can form an estimate of 
\begin_inset Formula $d\mbe_{\covdensnorm}\left[g\left(\theta\right)\right]/dt^{\trans}$
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $t=0$
